{"tid":388093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃埔花園男子　疑抹窗墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-09-05T07:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T01:00:27.000Z","uid":20933,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4236d3a9649128ee893fb57cff6977fd3bad03a7","tid":388093,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170905/large/1504595894_b5ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170905%2Flarge%2F1504595894_b5ce.jpg&h=65495be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅磡黃埔花園9期百合苑，下午1時23分，一名六旬男子由高處墮下，倒卧地下花槽。救護員將他送院，但告不治。警方到場封鎖現場，在花槽附近發現一條毛巾，警方其後到死者住所調查，發現窗邊有清潔用品，懷疑他抹窗時意外墮樓。死者的妻子此時從外回家，驚見大批警員在場，查問下驚悉丈夫墮樓，悲痛不已。"},{"pid":"89219e5cf57d2833c9f7cbdb054f2d7c9d08a24a","tid":388093,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:51:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170905&amp;guid=57171547&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170905%26guid%3D57171547%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=ExK9dujywAhJx97VqR7CPmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=39715f1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170905%26guid%3D57171547%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=62ea5250\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170905&amp;guid=57171547&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"b248eb252f6d5254fe4dec5500eb6a49630d0d81","tid":388093,"uid":11254,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"又一件"},{"pid":"df257f3ed0e670004cea4040d7039320f39b5132","tid":388093,"uid":9013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:52:48.000Z","msg":"我朋友係