aper/20170905/large/1504595894_b5ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170905%2Flarge%2F1504595894_b5ce.jpg&h=65495be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅磡黃埔花園9期百合苑，下午1時23分，一名六旬男子由高處墮下，倒卧地下花槽。救護員將他送院，但告不治。警方到場封鎖現場，在花槽附近發現一條毛巾，警方其後到死者住所調查，發現窗邊有清潔用品，懷疑他抹窗時意外墮樓。<span style=\"color: red;\">死者的妻子此時從外回家，驚見大批警員在場，查問下驚悉丈夫墮樓，悲痛不已</span>。</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係佢老婆陰毛？<br />\n<br />\n個老公跌撚死<br />\n<br />\n佢就賣樓再包條仔過世？</blockquote><br />\n陰你老母毛"},{"pid":"c819e090e15152d6056c174b580fdbe0ce3b7ebe","tid":388093,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a553948a088ab6f7b620a54eaf84c5f106c4fbe","tid":388093,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a3400e0792cbe79b1fc4cf28c100020ca63eb9","tid":388093,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/49e7x8qp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F49e7x8qp&h=f96c7f7a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7b9050cccbe414bff07d4aa5cdc3dd6cf369ed","tid":388093,"uid":46562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你班連登仔真係無撚用<br />\n個呀伯我老豆d同事<br />\n好撚支持雨傘革命同埋係黃絲<br />\n果陣有份落去支持<br />\n因為佢年齡大就廢老比人笑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵你班垃圾成班無民主</blockquote><br />\n你睇連登gathering就知果堆係咩人啦"},{"pid":"fed2447d4c24a9ad062a1c05c80de9f593074f26","tid":388093,"uid":57237,"like":1,"dislike":