，部分窗花已裝回窗花。警方正循是否與拆下窗花抹窗，而釀成意外墮樓調查。"},{"pid":"179e77c46e804b1a5ba3519dc5b2a0d05f5348d0","tid":388093,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是但啦<br />\n<br />\n托埋佢對腳上草叢, 鋪一鋪啲泥直接葬左佢算啦</blockquote><br />\n塵歸塵 土歸土"},{"pid":"9a865816805f605932e29378676895658a7e0375","tid":388093,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個窗抹都未抹過😂</blockquote><br />\n個窗開都未開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20cacf60f1ada9e924f63763fba769534e568c4","tid":388093,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你班連登仔真係無撚用<br />\n個呀伯我老豆d同事<br />\n好撚支持雨傘革命同埋係黃絲<br />\n果陣有份落去支持<br />\n因為佢年齡大就廢老比人笑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵你班垃圾成班無民主</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}